parameters: \knightGood to see you four made it here safely. Well,
as safe as can be in a place like this... the
\knightThankfully, my soldiers were able to locate what we
believe to be monster dens. If we're able to put some
pressure on them, the rate of monsters should slow down
long enough to get the civillians through safetly.
\knightMeanwhile, I'm busy getting this dirt out of the
way. It's quite a hassle, to say the least...
\knightSay, do you think you could give my soldiers a hand?
As soon as they clear those dens, they'll be able to
help me get this dirt out of the way.
\solOh, good to see you! I cleared out most of
this monster den, but I'm injured... you
four will need to deal with these three!
\solNice work. I'll be going to help shovel all that dirt by the exit.
\p2We've cleared both monster dens, let's go
see how much dirt is left at the exit.
\solYou will go no further! Our people will live!
